snippet.textDisplay:
The contrast between StarShah and Zeeshan is 👌🏻
StarShah′s lyrics are so well written and hit deep. You can tell he′s worked hard on the composition.

And when Zeeshan starts singing he just knocks it outta park.

It's been some time since I've heard him (Tere Jeha from Nescafe Basement still slaps), and I didn't recognize his face at first. But his signature, that high singing tone, is unmistakably a class in itself.

This 15th Season is something else.
